quran[6]{c,v,t,f}:
  6,103,"Àwọn ojú (ẹ̀dá) kò lè ká Allāhu. Òun sì ká àwọn ojú. Òun sì ni Aláàánú, Alámọ̀tán."
  6,104,"Ìmọ̀ àmọ̀dájú àti ẹ̀rí kúkú ti dé ba yín láti ọ̀dọ̀ Olúwa yín. Nítorí náà, ẹnikẹ́ni tó bá ríran, fún ẹ̀mí ara rẹ̀ ni. Ẹnikẹ́ni tó bá sì fọ́jú, fún ẹ̀mí ara rẹ̀ ni. Èmi kì í ṣe olùṣọ́ lórí yín."
  6,105,"Báyẹn ni A ṣe ń mú àwọn āyah wá lóníran-ànran ọ̀nà. - Kí wọ́n máa sọ pé, “O kẹ́kọ̀ọ́ (rẹ̀ lọ́dọ̀ àwọn onítírà ni.” Dípò kí wọ́n wí pé: “Wọ́n sọ̀ ọ́ kalẹ̀ fún ọ ni.”- (A mú un wá lóníran-ànran ọ̀nà sẹ́) nítorí kí A lè ṣàlàyé rẹ̀ fún àwọn ènìyàn tó nímọ̀. {1}",1:[Èsì ọ̀rọ̀ fún àwọn tó sọ bẹ́ẹ̀ ni sūrah an-Nahl;  16:103.]
  7,13,"(Allāhu) sọ pé: “Sọ̀kalẹ̀ kúrò níbí nítorí pé kò lẹ́tọ̀ọ́ fún ọ láti ṣègbéraga níbí. Nítorí náà, jáde dájúdájú ìwọ ń bẹ nínú àwọn ẹni yẹpẹrẹ.”"
  7,14,"(Èṣù) wí pé: “Lọ́ mi lára títí di ọjọ́ tí wọn yóò gbé àwọn ènìyàn dìde.”"
  7,15,"(Allāhu) sọ pé: “Dájúdájú ìwọ ń bẹ nínú àwọn tí A óò lọ́ lára.”"